{"tid":1820380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓國瑜票數落後原因曝光！名嘴：長輩早起投「票在箱底」","createTime":"2020-01-11T13:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T14:24:03.000Z","uid":5818,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"25d15c31aeb517a05798096bc8133e3ab0bdb8a1","tid":1820380,"uid":5818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"2020年中華民國總統大選，一開票民進黨候選人蔡英文就呈現大幅領先其他候選人。資深媒體人黃暐瀚在《中天新聞》的節目中，認為國民黨候選人韓國瑜會落後，是<span style=\"color: red;\">因為韓國瑜的票可能落在票匭底部「較晚開到票」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n黃暐瀚表示，許多長輩一大早就到投票所排隊投票，因此<span style=\"color: red;\">韓國瑜的票可能落在票匭底部</span>，較晚開到票，得票仍有「變化空間。」<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%A5%A8%E6%95%B8%E8%90%BD%E5%BE%8C%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%90%8D%E5%98%B4-%E9%95%B7%E8%BC%A9%E6%97%A9%E8%B5%B7%E6%8A%95-%E7%A5%A8%E5%9C%A8%E7%AE%B1%E5%BA%95-102826982.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2598%25B4-%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25BC%25A9%25E6%2597%25A9%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%258A%2595-%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E5%25BA%2595-102826982.html&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=5aa96e8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E7%A5%A8%E6%95%B8%E8%90%BD%E5%BE%8C%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E5%90%8D%E5%98%B4-%E9%95%B7%E8%BC%A9%E6%97%A9%E8%B5%B7%E6%8A%95-%E7%A5%A8%E5%9C%A8%E7%AE%B1%E5%BA%95-102826982.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZfVZX4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZfVZX4.png&h=584972b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/TatteredGrippingJunco-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FTatteredGri